---
import * as button from "primereact/button/button.esm";
const { Button } = button;
---

<div class="col-12 h-full flex flex-column justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-12 text-center text-5xl font-bold text-green-700">
    Providing our best IT services and solutions
  </div>
  <div class="col-12 grid justify-content-center sm:p-0 sx:p-0 p-4">
    <div
      class="flex flex-column xl:col-3 p-3 lg:col-6 md:col-12 bg-providing-card text-center m-6 zoom glassmorphism-card height-card"
    >
      <img class="product-img-wrapper" src="src/assets/images/Tablee.png" />
      <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-green-600">
        Application Development
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-900">
        ThinkShield Ltd. experience encompasses a broad range of technology
        products and application frameworks, and we are specialists in both
        development and integration.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-content-center">
        <Button
          className=" col-6  align-items-center text-green-500 hover:text-white  hover:bg-green-400 border-green-300 "
          label="For more details"
          text
          rounded
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-column xl:col-3 lg:col-6 md:col-12 bg-providing-card text-center m-6 zoom glassmorphism-card height-card overflow"
    >
      <img
        class="product-img-wrapper"
        src="src/assets/images/frame185562.jpg"
      />
      <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-green-600">Integration</div>
      <p class="text-xl text-green-900">
        Integration enables disparate systems to communicate, we follow best
        practice and standards supporting a number of messaging protocols
        including HL7 and FHIR
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-content-center">
        <Button
          className=" col-6  align-items-center text-green-500 hover:text-white  hover:bg-green-400 border-green-300 "
          label="For more details"
          text
          rounded
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-column xl:col-3 lg:col-6 md:col-12 bg-providing-card text-center m-6 zoom glassmorphism-card height-card overflow"
    >
      <img class="product-img-wrapper" src="src/assets/images/frame18556.jpg" />
      <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-green-600">
        Application Development
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
        We take pride in the solutions we offer and so like to provide our
        customers with support options that donâ€™t break the bank and fit their
        needs.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-content-center">
        <Button
          className=" col-6  align-items-center text-green-500 hover:text-white  hover:bg-green-400 border-green-300 "
          label="For more details"
          text
          rounded
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="col-12 text-center xl:text-3xl lg:text-xl md:text-md sm:text-sm sx:text-sx font-bold text-green-600"
  >
    We put our customers first, recognizing that security, data integrity,
    quality, efficiency, and cost are critical elements to delivering, not only
    successful IT Healthcare solutions, but also outstanding customer service.
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .bg-providing {
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
  }
  .bg-providing-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) !important;
  }
  .product-img-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .zoom {
    transition: transform 0.9s;
  }
  .glassmorphism-card {
    border-radius: 16px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(6.7px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6.7px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(85, 222, 173, 0.01);
  }
  .zoom:hover {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(55, 163, 86, 0.8);
  }
  .overflow {
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .height-card {
    min-height: 20vh;
  }
  .height-img {
    height: 40vh;
  }
</style>
